title: Pier of Peril 1951 - Warning! When you deal with these dames you're in the DANGER ZONE

sources.title: Pier of Peril 1951 - Warning! When you deal with these dames you're in the DANGER ZONE
sources.description:
Claire Underwood hires private-detective Dennis O’Brien to purchase a saxophone case at an auction. He wins the bid – only to be attacked instantly! Now he's racing to reclaim the case before its deadly secrets explode at a high-stakes yacht party.

Original title: Danger Zone (1951) 

Directed by William Berke

Main cast:
Hugh Beaumont - Dennis O'Brien
Tom Neal - Edgar Spadely
Edward Brophy - Prof. Frederick Simpson Schicker
Richard Travis - Police Lt. Bruger
Pamela Blake - Vicki Jason
Virginia Dale - Claire Underwood
Ralph Sanford - Larry Dunlap
Paula Drew - Sheila Jason
Jack Reitzen - Cole, the Auctioneer
Edward Clark - Elderly Man at Auction
Richard Monahan - Henry, the Bartender
Don Garner - Bud Becker
Tiny Jones - Woman at Auction

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/jAT6-R5ao2A
